message.entry: Invalid data type. First input argument must be single or double.
W must be a double or single vector of nonnegative weights, or a scalar 0 or 1.
The length of W must be compatible with X.
Invalid option. Option must be ''omitnan'', ''includenan'', ''omitmissing'' or ''includemissing''.
Invalid option. Option must be ''all'', ''omitnan'', ''includenan'', ''omitmissing'' or ''includemissing''.
Weight vector is only supported when the dimension is a positive integer scalar.
